headline: Jacobs to Continue Supporting One of California's Largest Water Reuse Projects
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) has been selected by LA Sanitation and Environment (LASAN) as the progressive design-build contractor for the Donald C. Tillman Advanced Water Equalization Basins, another critical part of the City of Los Angeles' long-term plans to increase recycled water production by 2035.
